Subject: [PATCH 3/8] spi: cadence-quadspi fix, cpld-spimux driver, and
 cpld-spimux fix

- spi: cadence-quadspi: fix indirect write timeout on Pensando Salina N1 (APB-AHB hazard)
- spi: add AMD Pensando Salina CPLD SPI multiplexer driver
- spi: cpld-spimux: Fix CPLD CSMAP write
