+config SPI_CPLD_SPIMUX
+	tristate "AMD Pensando Salina CPLD SPI mux"
+	depends on ARCH_PENSANDO_SALINA_SOC && SPI_MASTER
+	help
+	  This driver supports the CPLD-based SPI multiplexer
+	  present on AMD Pensando Salina platforms.
+
+	  The CPLD requires a register write on chip select 0
+	  to select the downstream SPI target before accessing
